Class SolTemp

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.SolTemp

  • public class SolTemp
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a model class represents a sol (1 sol represents one day which is equivalent to one 24 hours and 40 minutes of the Earth time) temperature of Mars.
    Author:
    Thermal Group (CS537: California State University, Los Angeles)
